HEADWORD: Batardeau
<hw>Ba`tar*deau"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>A cofferdam.</def> <rj><au>Brande & C.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
